Test Scenarios covered by automation :

In login-logout spec file, the test scenarios covered are:

1. Login to application successfully, validate the user name displayed 
    and print the user to console

2. Logout from application and 
    to validate if Signin title is displayed or not after successful logout 

In homepage-validation spec file, the scenarios covered are:

1. Login to application, search for a product and 
   select the quantity from dropdown and add item to cart.
   After adding item to cart successfully, also validating if added item and quantity are present in the cart.

2. Removing an item from cart and validating if item is removed from the cart.
